    {
      "id": "PopularPost214751",
      "post_content": "**@Breaking this in Standard, as of 12/3/2011:**  \nI had this big, long, thoughtful post about what kinds of cards we should look out for if we want to break [Nim Deathmantle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nim Deathmantle), but then I found something very simple. It requires a huge board commitment but only one *specific* card.  \n  \n***[Village Bell-Ringer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Village Bell-Ringer)***  \n  \nMana-Dorks:  \n[Avacyn's Pilgrim](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Avacyn's Pilgrim)  \n[Birds of Paradise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Birds of Paradise)  \n[Deranged Assistant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Deranged Assistant)  \n[Llanowar Elves](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Llanowar Elves)  \n[Elvish Archdruid](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elvish Archdruid)  \n[Alloy Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Alloy Myr)  \n[Plague Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Myr)  \n[Palladium Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Palladium Myr)  \n[Gold Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gold Myr)  \n[Silver Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Silver Myr)  \n[Leaden Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leaden Myr)  \n[Iron Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Iron Myr)  \n[Copper Myr](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Copper Myr)  \n  \nFree Sac-Engines:  \n[Devouring Swarm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Devouring Swarm) (infinitely large flying creature)  \n[Flesh-Eater Imp](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flesh-Eater Imp) (infinitely large flying/infect creature)  \n... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Ragamander",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost214751\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\"><b>@Breaking this in Standard, as of 12/3/2011:</b><br/>I had this big, long, thoughtful post about what kinds of cards we should look out for if we want to break <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nim Deathmantle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nim Deathmantle\">Nim Deathmantle</a>, but then I found something very simple. It requires a huge board commitment but only one <i>specific</i> card.<br/><br/><i><b><u><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Village Bell-Ringer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Village Bell-Ringer\">Village Bell-Ringer</a></u></b></i><br/><br/>Mana-Dorks:<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Avacyn's Pilgrim\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Avacyn's Pilgrim\">Avacyn's Pilgrim</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Birds of Paradise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Birds of Paradise\">Birds of Paradise</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Deranged Assistant\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Deranged Assistant\">Deranged Assistant</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Llanowar Elves\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Llanowar Elves\">Llanowar Elves</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Elvish Archdruid\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elvish Archdruid\">Elvish Archdruid</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Alloy Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Alloy Myr\">Alloy Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Plague Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Myr\">Plague Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Palladium Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Palladium Myr\">Palladium Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gold Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gold Myr\">Gold Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Silver Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Silver Myr\">Silver Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Leaden Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leaden Myr\">Leaden Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Iron Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Iron Myr\">Iron Myr</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Copper Myr\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Copper Myr\">Copper Myr</a><br/><br/>Free Sac-Engines:<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Devouring Swarm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Devouring Swarm\">Devouring Swarm</a> (infinitely large flying creature)<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Flesh-Eater Imp\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flesh-Eater Imp\">Flesh-Eater Imp</a> (infinitely large flying/infect creature)<br/>... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 214751)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '214751'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy13722\">Ragamander</span>\r\n                                (12/3/2011 11:34:55 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl